Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:07.19,ED01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}Futari arukidasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:05.94,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy is a science where one understands the structure of matter, breaks it down, then rebuilds it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:11.53,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,However, it is not an all-powerful technique,\Nas one cannot create something out of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:17.66,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,If one wishes to gain something,\None must present something of equal value.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:22.08,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,This is the concept of equivalent exchange, the fundamental basis of alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:26.71,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is a taboo in alchemy. Human transmutation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:29.42,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,One must not commit this act.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:08.31,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,The First Branch of the National Central Library, where Marcoh's research data was kept, was burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:16.03,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Ed and Al obtain the research data with the help of Sheska, a former librarian. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The ingredients of philosopher's stones...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...are live humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:28.12,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Seeking more of the truth, Ed and Al sneak into the abandoned Research Laboratory 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:45.18,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty fast for a guy so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.43,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Else it wouldn't be fun for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:48.64,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.31,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Number 66.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:54.27,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,That's just my work name, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:58.69,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,I'll dismantle you neatly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.99,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,so go ahead and wail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:14.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:17.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be what's used to transmute philosopher's stones?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.84,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:24.64,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, but I'm amazed you figured\Nthat out by just looking at the transmutation circle, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:32.06,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,My duty is to guard this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.81,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I'll introduce myself as Number 48.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.23,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not an old man, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:45.45,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,I've been instructed to eliminate any outsiders who have infiltrated the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.53,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think badly of me, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:48.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:54.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it too badly when you get beaten by a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.96,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,An alchemist, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.80,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how good you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:06.14,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like that arm saved your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:10.47,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,But my beloved sword even slices through steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:26.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not have a body in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:28.28,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:31.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I spar with someone like you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:36.25,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so there's someone in this state in the outside world, too, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:45.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That there's some idiot other than me who'd come up with the idea of affixing a soul to a suit of armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.80,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:52.06,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,48 was my death row number.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:59.56,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,When I still had my body, I was called Slicer the Homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Death row. Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:08.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this place makes philosopher's stones out of criminals on death row, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.62,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,That I cannot answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:17.21,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,I was simply hired for my skills, given this body,\Nand stationed here as a watchdog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:22.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Which means there's a seal somewhere that mediates the soul and the armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.34,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.76,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,This seal of blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:31.89,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,If you destroy it, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're awfully kind to let me in on your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:40.81,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the type that seeks thrills in fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:44.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're so kind, want to let me off the hook?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Was that worth a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:52.58,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think a murderer is just going to let his prey get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.75,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:58.71,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Like~I~said~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.96,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Elicia's having her third birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:05.92,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Colonel Hughes, I'm working right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.93,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence! So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.43,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, she's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:15.68,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! Quit calling me about your daughter all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.52,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,And with an army line, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.06,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Not just my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.31,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud of my wife, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.94,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right, I'll listen to your story, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:31.32,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,About your cute and charming "Scar" you're so proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.58,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We've found several unidentified bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:39.58,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,They're pretty decomposed, so it's\Ndifficult to determine if he's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:47.30,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,There haven't been any sightings of him in the East,\Nso as of now, most people believe he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:51.76,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, we can probably set\Nthe Elric brothers free of their escorts soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:55.22,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Is Major Armstrong still in charge of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:58.81,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, apparently the Major's subordinates have taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.02,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,They got us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.77,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,I knew they were being too quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:09.40,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Major Armstrong's going to kill us for dereliction of duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:13.07,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Those brats! They should put themselves in their escorts' shoes every once in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:14.70,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.03,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.45,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.45,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,The former Research Laboratory 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Something doesn't feel right in my shoulder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:40.23,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,...this time so it would be more resistant to rust,\Nbut that makes it less durable, so don't overuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't settle this quick...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.43,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,You're almost like a monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.43,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had worthy prey like you in a while. I'm delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:25.40,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,But with your wounds and fatigue, the outcome is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:30.61,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,My companion should have disposed of your companion by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:34.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Is your companion strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:38.83,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,He is. Weaker than me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:48.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No worries there, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:53.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in a lot of fights with him\Nsince we were little, and I've never won.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:06.14,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, stay still and let me cut you, hippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.16,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That body...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.41,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a few circumstances of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:26.46,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, let me tell you a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.67,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of him, too, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:32.05,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,A middle-aged man by the name of Barry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:40.35,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,A long, long time ago, there was a middle-aged man here in Central named Barry who loved to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:44.18,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Barry loved to cut up meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:48.77,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, it got to the point he couldn't satisfy himself with just beef and pork,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:53.57,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,so he started to go out into the city during nighttime to cut up humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:10:02.70,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Barry was eventually caught, but the number of people who fell victim to him was twenty-three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:10.00,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,After terrorizing the hell out of the residents of Central, he was sentenced to death by hanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.13,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,And everyone lived happily ever after...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:17.22,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,...is the story given to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.84,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,But there's actually a sequel to the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:22.76,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Barry isn't actually dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:25.64,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive and has been assigned to watch over a certain somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:28.39,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Though he's had his body taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:38.99,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The man standing in front of you right now is the infamous serial killer, Barry the Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.36,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I've never heard of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.58,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I was born in the countryside in the East, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:50.25,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but even if you've never heard the story, shouldn't you give some kind of reaction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.08,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Something like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:54.09,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,"AHHHH!", or "What's with that body?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.84,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,AHHHH! W-W-W-What's with that body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.13,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.26,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you were sentenced to death, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.35,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Scaring me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.39,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:08.10,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:10.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I've had a few circumstances of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:15.61,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,My older brother affixed my soul when I lost my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:16.69,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.65,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Your brother, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.57,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:26.03,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys really brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:28.54,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, our personalities are different, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.79,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. No, no, no, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:35.79,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,What I meant to say was, maybe you're\Nan armor doll your "brother" created?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.75,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.51,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Does your real human self really exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:41.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:45.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Alphonse Elric, a human! No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.31,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.93,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have memories from when I was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:53.31,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,What if those were created, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But Winry and Granny...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.73,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably in on it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.90,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.41,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't exist to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:08.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then... what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:09.95,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.71,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! This place is restric-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:15.75,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:19.13,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,I love hacking live humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:22.34,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,I love to kill, and I can't get enough of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:25.14,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,I exist to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:28.93,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only proof I need to know that I am who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.52,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,So your little brother is that strong, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:39.36,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Then I had better defeat you quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:47.24,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.91,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,How foul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Like there are rules in a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:06.68,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? My blood seal isn't broken yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.43,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and dest-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.22,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,About the philosopher's stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:16.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Spill everything you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.06,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,No can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:20.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, the loser shouldn't be putting on a brave front.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.40,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,I... haven't lost yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:28.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:41.84,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to mention it. Slicer the Homicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.46,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,...Was actually a duo of brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:46.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The head and body are two different people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:52.68,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,And who's the one who said there aren't any rules in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:56.81,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for Round 2, runt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me a runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:01.77,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I'm not going to give you time for a transmutation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, I lost too much blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to feel dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.17,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,This is it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:33.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:36.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Making me remember that jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:39.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I just did the same thing he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.48,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone and done it now, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:44.32,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.82,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,It's shameful, but we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:51.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to say something like, "Hey, we're actually a trio", are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.16,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,We won't, we won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:56.74,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Just destroy us already, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me from having to murder someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.25,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,You consider us human?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:11.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't accept you two as human,\Nit would mean I'm doing the same to my brother, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:15.76,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, what's wrong, armor doll?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:18.14,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an armor doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:19.98,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.48,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really exist to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.86,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:29.44,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,There's a way to prove you're not an armor doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.24,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a blood seal, too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.74,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Erase it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.83,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,If you die, you were human!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.75,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,If you're still movin', then you're an armor doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:43.29,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.88,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll do it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,My little brother is human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So are you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't want to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:00.56,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:07.23,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Us two have been stealing, destroying,\Nand murdering ever since we came of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:12.74,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,And we're being treated as humans for the first time, after being turned into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.32,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:18.95,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you everything as a parting gift, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:24.29,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,The one who created the philosopher's stone and told us to guard this place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:34.01,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:39.68,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be talking about things like that, 48.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:43.89,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the Fullmetal runt doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.10,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,What a troublesome child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.40,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find out about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:53.28,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.03,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,BROTHER!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:59.41,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:03.71,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were about to kill a precious sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.00,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:09.04,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What were you gonna do if you screwed up the plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.34,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by sacrifice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:35.53,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? This runt is ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Quit calling me a runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:42.74,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,A runt's a runt, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.62,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.21,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts if you get injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:52.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat you to a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:57.88,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:01.14,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.81,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing your arm broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.98,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to suffer any other injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.90,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:15.74,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget you're being kept alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:20.24,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be troublesome if a boy like this\Nhappens to find this place again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:23.33,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Let's burn it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:30.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... there's something I've always wanted to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...but I've been too scared to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What was Brother trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:38.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,"Something he was too scared to say?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.14,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Something he was too scared to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:45.39,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,...maybe you're an armor doll your "brother" created?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.85,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Does your real human self really exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:54.98,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, armor dollie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.45,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Just accept it. It'll make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.41,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,You're full of openings, hippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:10.92,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:12.00,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.54,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Just surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:18.09,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.35,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant... evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.07,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.28,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:41.49,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But Brother's still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:42.95,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.99,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this leaves me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.91,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll just get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:49.08,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.79,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,You guys better run, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.29,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:53.21,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.08,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.92,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get caught in it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:56.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.55,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Howdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.59,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,A package for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:05.97,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:14.19,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't in danger or anything, but he lost a lot of blood, so get him to a hospital quick, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:19.28,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, and make sure you guys keep an eye on him so he doesn't do anything too reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.61,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He's an important guy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:22.70,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:24.61,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lt. Ross, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.45,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant, lend me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.49,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,He's covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:31.08,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk later! You'd better get out of here, too-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.75,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:42.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:44.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You plannin' on lettin' us die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.68,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Pipe down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.85,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:56.56,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,This is the sound of a building crumbling due to explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:01.69,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the proximity... it's probably Research Laboratory 5 next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:05.45,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what a nice sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:08.82,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It shakes me to my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:11.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your trap, Kimbley!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:13.20,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:18.42,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It reminded me of the Ishbal Extermination, and it just made me so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:33.18,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,...maybe you're an armor doll your "brother" created?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:11.41,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,And so, about Central...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:17.20,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,The bigwigs who oversee State Alchemists are going through a labor shortage thanks to Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:18.54,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:22.88,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor is it won't be long before\NColonel Mustang is invited to Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:24.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Central, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:25.88,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:27.55,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:31.68,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,If you manage to get to the top at that age,\Nyou'll gain a lot of enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:34.30,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:38.18,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Words of wisdom from your senior in Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:42.73,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Have a lot of people who understand and are willing to support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:43.94,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:46.19,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:47.57,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,None of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:51.70,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd he hang up on me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:55.24,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Colonel Hughes, please keep personal calls to a minimum!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:56.78,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:03.21,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric hesitates to speak his words...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:07.21,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,...and Alphonse Elric becomes perplexed by Barry's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:13.63,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,The one certainty is that a girl's memories hold the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.64,0:24:18.60,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.60,0:24:21.60,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 9, Created Feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.35,0:24:26.52,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Their hearts waver because they put their trust in each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.52,0:24:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
